            "faq_title": "How long does my child need to brush?",
            "faq_des": "<p>Just 30 to 60 seconds is all it takes. Because the U-shaped head cleans all teeth simultaneously, it achieves in one minute what a manual toothbrush takes two to three minutes to accomplish.<br/><br/></p>"
